Create and Share an App from a CRM Analytics Template

To create and manage CRM Analytics apps: Manage CRM Analytics Templated Apps

Navigate to Analytics Studio. Click Create, then select App. Alternatively, click Template Gallery.

Select a template. Answer the questions on each page of the wizard. Name your app and click Create.

The creation process takes a few minutes. You can view the status on the next page. After it's complete, refresh the page to see your app.

To troubleshoot any app creation issues, use the App Install History Page in Setup.

Now that you've created the app, share it with users in your organization. Open your app and click the Share icon at upper right.

In the next screen, use the search field under Invite others: to find other users in your org. Select whether you want to make the selected user a Viewer, Editor, or Manager of the app.
